---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About – Bliss Dermacare" description="Meet the team behind Bliss Dermacare. Florida-licensed estheticians with 7+ years of experience serving Pebble Creek, Wesley Chapel, and the Tampa Bay area.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-[#faf9f7] border-b border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4 block">Our Story</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">About Bliss Dermacare</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600">Built on science, delivered with care — right here in Pebble Creek, FL.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden col-span-2 h-64 lg:h-80">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6663366/pexels-photo-6663366.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Bliss Dermacare studio" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden h-44">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5069377/pexels-photo-5069377.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" alt="Treatment in progress" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden h-44">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519824145371-296894a0daa9?w=400&h=350&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Professional skincare" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-3 block">Who We Are</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif text-neutral-900 leading-tight">Professional skincare done right.</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">At Bliss Dermacare, we believe great skin starts with great science and genuine care. We're a Florida-licensed skincare studio based in Pebble Creek, combining proven techniques with personalized treatment plans built around your unique skin.</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Whether you're tackling acne, hyperpigmentation, signs of aging, or just want a consistent glow — every session is tailored to your specific goals, never a generic template.</p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 py-6 border-y border-neutral-100">
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-1">FL</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wide">Licensed<br/>Esthetician</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center border-x border-neutral-100">
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-1">7+</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wide">Years of<br/>Experience</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-1">5.0★</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wide">Average Client<br/>Rating</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              1-on-1 Personalized Care
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              Science-Backed Formulas
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              Pebble Creek, FL
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section id="why-us" class="py-16 bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-3 block">Why Clients Choose Us</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-3">No shortcuts. No cookie-cutter treatments.</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-600">We care about long-term skin health, not just one good session.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-neutral-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Personalized Every Time</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Your skin is assessed at every appointment. The treatment adapts to how your skin is behaving that day — not a preset menu item.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-neutral-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Professional-Grade Products</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">We use medical-grade, clinically tested products — not what you find off the shelf. Real results come from real formulations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-neutral-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Building Long-Term Results</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">We're not here for one good session. We track your progress, adjust when needed, and help you build a home care routine that sticks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Book CTA -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">Let's get started.</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-8">Not sure which treatment is right for you? Schedule a free skin assessment and we'll build a plan together.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/book/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all font-medium shadow-sm">Book an Appointment</a>
        <a href="/memberships/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-primary-300 text-primary-700 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-50 transition-all font-medium">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"/></svg>
          Membership Plans
        </a>
        <a href="/consultation/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-neutral-300 text-neutral-700 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full hover:border-primary-400 hover:text-primary-600 transition-all font-medium">Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
